201
00:14:32,467 --> 00:14:34,317
Yumeko...

202
00:14:38,047 --> 00:14:42,167
Go ahead and explain. I'm listening.

203
00:14:53,477 --> 00:14:59,337
I told you that Aoi is my childhood friend and comrade.

204
00:14:59,907 --> 00:15:03,647
But I was avoiding Aoi and didn't want to face her feelings.

205
00:15:03,647 --> 00:15:07,587
Even though I'm aware of her feelings for me.

206
00:15:07,587 --> 00:15:09,167
That's why...

207
00:15:10,465 --> 00:15:12,455
this is my fault.

208
00:15:13,697 --> 00:15:19,767
Also, I should have told you earlier about the manga.

209
00:15:20,317 --> 00:15:24,877
I came to Tokyo, with a dream of being a manga artist.

210
00:15:25,717 --> 00:15:28,087
I managed to debut somehow,

211
00:15:29,407 --> 00:15:32,367
but I couldn't draw a story that I was satisfied with.

212
00:15:33,487 --> 00:15:36,117
The more I panicked,

213
00:15:36,117 --> 00:15:39,287
I more I didn't know what to draw.

214
00:15:40,547 --> 00:15:45,587
At that moment, I met you, Yumeko.

215
00:15:46,357 --> 00:15:53,049
Initially, I wrote the story about you and me for my own sake.

216
00:15:54,497 --> 00:15:59,307
But when I tried my luck and showed it to the editor,

217
00:16:00,597 --> 00:16:03,537
