218
00:16:04,237 --> 00:16:07,157
<i>Your new story is not bad.</i>

219
00:16:07,157 --> 00:16:10,217
<i>Themes with love contracts are not uncommon,</i>

220
00:16:10,217 --> 00:16:12,077
<i>but the heroine is lively,</i>

221
00:16:12,077 --> 00:16:16,637
<i>and the on-off relationship between the two is not bad at all.</i>

222
00:16:16,637 --> 00:16:18,657
